---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — txlab.cash">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-10">
    <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-bch-500 font-mono font-semibold">
      // The site
    </div>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-fg">
      What is <span class="text-bch-500 font-mono font-medium tracking-tight">txlab.cash</span>?
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-fg-mid leading-relaxed">
      A tech-focused hub for the Bitcoin Cash network — plus the best
      maintained map of the projects being built, run, and used on it.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-14 space-y-8 text-fg-mid leading-relaxed">
    <div>
      <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neon-400 font-mono font-semibold">
        // The pitch
      </div>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Come for the Lab, stay for the Map.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3">
        The Transaction Lab is where you build, sign, and inspect a BCH
        transaction — in three modes: simulated (learn), chipnet (try safely),
        mainnet (watch your own). No wallet install, no keys leaving your
        browser, no fake abstractions.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3">
        The Map is a curated registry of what's alive on BCH — every entry
        tagged with a freshness state and a last-verified date, so you know
        what's maintained and what isn't.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neon-400 font-mono font-semibold">
        // What we are not
      </div>
      <p class="mt-2">
        <strong class="text-fg">Not a price site.</strong> There is no ticker,
        no market cap, no "will BCH moon" — the questions the ecosystem has
        already answered a thousand times.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3">
        <strong class="text-fg">Not the official voice of BCH.</strong> There
        is no such thing. BCH is a network with independent node
        implementations, independent wallet teams, and independent client
        libraries. This site is one community-run view — useful, we hope, but
        not authoritative.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3">
        <strong class="text-fg">Not for sale.</strong> No sponsored placements,
        no boosted cards, no affiliate cuts. See the{" "}
        <a href="/editorial-principles" class="prose-link text-fg">editorial principles</a>{" "}
        for the full commitment.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neon-400 font-mono font-semibold">
        // Who runs it
      </div>
      <p class="mt-2">
        The site was started and is maintained by{" "}
        <a
          href="https://github.com/BitFaced2"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="prose-link text-fg">BitFaced</a>. The registry, pages, and
        design tokens all live in{" "}
        <a
          href="https://github.com/BitFaced2/txlab.cash"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="prose-link text-fg">a public repo</a>{" "}
        — every project entry is a YAML file you can audit, correct, or
        translate via pull request.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3">
        The design language borrows from{" "}
        <a
          href="https://github.com/BitFaced2/bchn-dirty"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="prose-link text-fg">BCHN Dirty</a>'s
        <code class="font-mono text-bch-400">cypher.qss</code> palette — one
        visual identity across the BCH tooling built here.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-line bg-surface p-8 md:p-10">
      <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neon-400 font-mono font-semibold">
        // Next
      </div>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-fg">
        Something to add? Something wrong?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-fg-mid leading-relaxed">
        The site is a work in progress. If you see a project that's missing,
        a freshness state that's wrong, or a page that could be clearer —
        the fastest way to fix it is a PR.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          href="/contribute"
          class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-bch-500 text-canvas text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-bch-400 transition-colors">
          How to contribute
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/BitFaced2/txlab.cash"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-line-mid text-sm font-medium text-fg-mid hover:border-bch-500 hover:text-bch-400 transition-colors">
          Repo on GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
